            "title": "簡訊：收入兩年暴增150倍 思格新能源招股籌最多44億港元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QP8Vj5Ur1QRu4VT5_SWD7g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/the_bamboo_works_186/d26062cd0a40d3c953dcf44edb0575c2\" width=\"500\"/></div></figure></div>",
